{"tid":1733492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【催淚彈放題】生酮女皇提醒網民 B12a可以中和山埃毒","createTime":"2019-11-18T06:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T07:59:45.000Z","uid":124722,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12136a23f47508bfde6ad768b472bf30aba8bd20","tid":1733492,"uid":124722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191118/60280379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191118%2F60280379&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2UtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=e353fb8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191118%2F60280379&h=6dbf0bb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191118/60280379</a><br />\n<br />\n香港抗爭運動持續5個月，當權者繼續漠視民意，持續「旨暴製亂」，向抗爭者發射催淚彈數量，每天以千計，令人震驚。近日有網民瘋傳吃維他命B12可解毒，排走二噁英等有害物質，但已有學者證實完全沒有幫助。<br />\n不時在網上教授各種健康療法、五年前亦有出動為前線煮飯兼送餐的「生酮女皇」，今日在其FB專頁「FOURum」轉發相關報道，籲大眾要留意。<br />\n今日「生酮女皇」接受《蘋果》訪問說：「其實上個星期我都有拍片同網民講得，B12a Hydroxocobalamin係可以中和山埃，而唔係二噁英，而B12a Hydroxocobalamin亦唔係普通B12，唔好搞錯。」<br />\n近日催淚彈每天「放題」，「生酮女皇」指港人日復日吸入不少山埃毒，「催淚煙入面有山埃，當然係二噁英最多，但日日吸山埃，其實我哋係慢性中毒，而B12a Hydroxocobalamin同山埃結合，就可以成為身體用到嘅B12，叫做有更好嘅保障，素食者就更加需要。」"},{"pid":"fbca13b8e68447fed982cdb6e1e49e6f1e91f3a0","tid":1733492,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:17:17.000Z","msg":"有化學學者講左對二惡英無用啦"},{"pid":"0e644359873e11be79306357988a3634ea1f5e5c","tid":1733492,"uid":23187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"佢去咗踩k kwong facebook踩場 笑鬼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b22d2612ff96ce4cd1e4f9c088d89b079ac513","tid":1733492,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"弱智先會信"},{"pid":"6a80c4cf6e67614923e4da4176b13e4b14070833","tid":1733492,"uid":295602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"on9有個譜<br />\n山埃咁易搞掂就唔會嚴陣以待"}]}